{"tid":1336722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有和理非 今日行完留耐啲","createTime":"2019-07-21T05:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T08:13:16.000Z","uid":192540,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd97d912375e6ef33e8670ed74832eb31c2fea40","tid":1336722,"uid":192540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"警方縮短遊行路線 就係想你班唔攪事嘅人行完拿拿臨散 盡快減低示威者總人數 減低夜晚圍捕餘下嘅人嘅難度<br />\n唔係要你地行完熱屎辣辣響路中心企多幾個鐘等警方驅散同食椒<br />\n但真心想你地繼續留響附近安全地方食花生 涼下冷氣<br />\n或者返銅鑼灣行下街又好 坐低食個tea又好<br />\n再唔係hea多陣食完晚飯再落街散下步<br />\n換走黑衫 做返普通市民去，屌狗<br />\n多一個人留低 就多一分力量<br />\n唔使衝 唔使守 甚至可以咩都唔幫手<br />\n但一定要留 不散<br />\n陣間見"},{"pid":"abec90f2c6c869b7cb0b74075edb3d8bc34ee1f9","tid":1336722,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3812e2b9409bfd3ec0a976f2ab276c9b76305b94","tid":1336722,"uid":214029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e427b7147bee4412c0491e92c8fd2760220d0336","tid":1336722,"uid":51023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"518fb64620371d4b206da4238888e0460a7e7bf3","tid":1336722,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留守港島 休息恢復體力 留意事態發展</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ce682be6a253dce0c37cab4b50da1bf378ec716","tid":1336722,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"push,光復香港"},{"pid":"f04b53eeb49bb5ec39a71cb11b93863efa21d2c2","tid":1336722,"uid":213111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"衝擊之前記得買好台灣機票，聽日就飛"},{"pid":"9c2e645f239dad34e974825ee84d0e227aa94635","tid":1336722,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"可以係附近食個飯休息先<img src=\"/assets/fa